{
  "stem": "1753.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In one of the other areas that I related earlier, for example, when I was doing business outside the ghetto, and I smuggled myself out every day, I went to the most affluent-looking areas, where the well-to-do Poles, or ethnic Germans, or Germans even lived.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those are the houses that are in-- because it was an area where you wanted to sell parsley wholesale and parsley retail.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those spices.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sure enough, I had one customer that-- that had a store, a Pole, in the-- on the ground floor of that relatively new building, one of the few buildings that wasn't destroyed during the blitzkrieg in 1939.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he said, 'Meet me upstairs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I pay you upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't have much money down here.' So I followed him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was on the top floor, I believe on the 12th floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Went up with the elevator.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then he paid me, and I walked down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't want to take the elevator.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And on the 11th floor of that building, there was an SS headquarters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as I come down that first flight of stairs, sure enough, there was an SS man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he tells me, oh, you-- in German it's, [GERMAN SPEECH], but it's slang German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, 'You-- you-- you Polack, go down.' And I stupidly said to myself, 'But I'm not a Polack.' He said, 'So what are you?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Are you a Jew?' I said, 'No.'",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I spoke German, perfect German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so he said, [GERMAN], it means documents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sure enough, I had my-- my-- a document from Germany, when I left Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I changed from where it says Israelite.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I changed it to Catholic.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
